05:30.683 --> 05:31.443
Qu Mingcheng

05:31.523 --> 05:33.162
takkan terlepas hukuman undang-undang.

05:34.003 --> 05:35.123
Sandiwara ini

05:35.402 --> 05:36.763
akhirnya tamat.

05:38.402 --> 05:40.042
Tanpa penglibatan peribadi kamu,

05:40.563 --> 05:41.802
